the main purpose of this driver is to control transceivers and access their info

the brief description of related  modules are listed bellow
<sff.ko>
manager, it hangles fsm and related control, and provide sysfs interface and use the driver api provided by sff_platform
<sff_platform.ko>
it can be considered as sff driver , it hides hardare dependent features from sff (ex: eeprom i2c topology , io expander.. etc)
it provide sysfs interface as well, the main purpose is for hardware validation
and it use io api exported by sff_io.ko

<sff_io.ko>
it handle io pin control through pca 9555  

sff_platform .ko and sff_io.ko may be combined as one , so far keep them separated 

